snippet.title: Forget What You Heard:  Punching exists in Pekiti Tirsia Kali
snippet.description:
Join us in the next Pekiti Tirsia Global training camp!  Check the schedule for Bali, Indonesia and Spain for 2018 here: http://teampekiti.com/calendar/


Not only is there punching in Pekiti Tirsia Kali, Tuhon Jared is taking it on a whole new level by recruiting the help of world class striking coaches to get it down to a science!

In this video, Faii Falamoe an MMA Striking coach trains Tuhon Jared Wihonig and helps him develop some standardized combinations and drills.

Follow Aperture on Facebook: http://bit.ly/2t1hXGe
Exclusive Videos and Fight Gear: http://ApertureFightFocused.com



Follow the Entire Aperture Team!

Ryan Hoover: https://www.facebook.com/RyanHooverFTF
Eli Knight: https://www.youtube.com/eliknight173
Jared Wihongi: https://www.facebook.com/jared.wihongi
Buck Grant: https://www.instagram.com/buckgrant
Amber Stak: https://www.instagram.com/amberthize
JD Caputo: https://www.modern-pankration.com/
GN: https://www.instagram.com/GN_Funkertactical/




_


All of our videos are for educational and entertainment purposes only.  Please do not try any of the actions you see in our videos.  Train under the qualified guidance of an instructor.  Consult your physician.  Listen to your body.  Understand your limitations and capabilities.  Have fun.  Hope to see you in one of our seminars!

Get notified of training events in your area: http://bit.ly/2t5KdHZ
